metadata.description:
Caesary (http://www.lekool.com) is a free to play online browser-based MMORTS game based on Roman Empire history where you create a city, get contracts, manage your workers, train your army and recruit heroes to conquer land and achieve glory, similar to Evony, but better. Caesary is a browser based game, which means no download is required.

www.lekool.com

Caesary is based on the history of the Roman Empire, the post-Republican phase of the ancient Roman civilization, characterized by an autocratic form of government and large territorial holdings in Europe and around the Mediterranean. The term is used to describe the Roman state during and after the time of the first emperor, Augustus.
